<p>The post-hoc tests indicate that, after Bonferroni correction for multip=
le testing, the following differences are significant (adjusted p &lt; 0.05=
).
</p>
<ul><li>Month 5 vs Months 7 and 8</li>
<li>Month 9 vs Months 7 and 8</li></ul>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Implementation">Implementat=
ion</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracke=
t">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DKruskal%=
E2%80%93Wallis_test&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D6" title=3D"Edit sectio=
n: Implementation"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-brack=
et">]</span></span></div>
<p>The Kruskal=E2=80=93Wallis test can be implemented in many programming t=
ools and languages. We list here only the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.o=
rg/wiki/Open_source" title=3D"Open source">open source</a> free software pa=
ckages:
</p>
<ul><li>In <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Python_(programming_lan=
guage)" title=3D"Python (programming language)">Python</a>'s <a href=3D"htt=
